-- Uganda to Send 1,800 Specialized Troops to Somalia, Daily Monitor Reports
-- B y   F r e d   O j a m b o
-- 2010-12-23T06:42:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-23/uganda-to-send-1-800-specialized-troops-to-somalia-daily-monitor-reports.html
Uganda plans to send 1,800 troops
that specialize in urban warfare to Somalia, with the first
group leaving in January to replace a contingent that has
concluded their term, Daily Monitor reported, citing Katumba
Wamala, the Commander of Land Forces.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fred Ojambo in Kampala at 
 fojambo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  